Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just supposed to be an ordinary third grader,\N but then a small incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I received was a courageous heart.\N What I gained were magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've crossed paths many times, yet... we still\N don't really know anything about each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to hear your answer,\N and because I want to know you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.04,0:00:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I've decided that I'll confront you directly\N and shake off my hesitation...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and just believe in the magic within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.38,0:01:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three... return to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, for Nanoha-san and Yuuno-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you both will be getting a lecture from\N me personally on your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's Separate Heart-felt Vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.68,0:03:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following orders doesn't affect a single\N person, but an entire group of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is that the selfish actions you took\N could have affected not only yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it could have also affected the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this were a normal case, you both could\N expect severe punishments, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...taking your magnificent results into account,\N we'll overlook your actions this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not do this a second time. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then... the big problem starts now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chrono, have you learned anything about\N the incident, even superficial data?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Amy, please transmit it to the monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The mage hailing from the same place\N as us, Midchilda, Precia Testarossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her field of study is in the development of energy\N sources allowing one to traverse dimensional space.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being a great mage...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she was involved in an accident while doing\N illegal research, and was thus exiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The data we already have about her and the data\N from the magical assault earlier both match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... that girl named Fate is most likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate-chan. Back then, she said "Mother"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother and daughter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... rather than being surprised...\N she seemed to be more frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amy! Are you able to pull up any more\N details about this Precia woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like where she went after being exiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or anything about her familial relationships?\N Anything at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I'll look into it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This woman... is Fate-chan's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having that opportunity right in front of your face\N and squandering it, mindlessly ignoring them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too cruel, Fate.\N Do you really want to fill me with grief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precia Testarossa... according to Midchildian records...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she was the third director of the Central Science\N & Development Bureau twenty-six years ago, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was also privately working on a thesis involving\N energy sources allowing the traversal of dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the concepts of this "Hydra" thesis were tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She conducted her experiment with illegal\N materials... and the experiment failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The results included a mid-scale dimensional\N disturbance at the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which caused the fissuring of the entire central\N area, eventually engulfing the surrounding areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.53,0:06:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there was a large\N dispute about the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...saying that the failure didn't\N exceed her expectations...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that there was nothing illegal\N about the materials used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She moved many times after that, continuing\N to perform her secret projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point, the records\N lost track of her whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's about all I can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her family ties and her actions\N up to the point when she went missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That data was completely erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, the main office is putting\N together a file on that data for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will that take to prepare?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said about a day or two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that Precia woman and Fate-chan are able\N to release that much magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can't afford to act hastily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we still have to repair Asura's\N shielding system, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you two should take some time to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, Nanoha-san. It's not good\N for you to miss school all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.64,0:07:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll approve a return trip for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a good idea to see your family and\N make an appearance at school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.61,0:07:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate! Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate! Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cause a dimensional disturbance with these,\N but I won't be able to reach Alhazred...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no more time... neither me nor Alicia...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're her mother, and she's your daughter, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's working so hard for you...\N She's doing everything she can for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.47,0:08:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you keep doing those cruel things to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is certainly inept at creating familiars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see she imbued this one with far\N too many unnecessary emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate is your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All she wants is to see you smile,\N to return to your old, kind self... that's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... who are nothing but an intrusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't matter where... but I have\N to transport myself somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Fate... just wait a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate. Wake up, Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the nine Jewel Seeds you've\N managed to collect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the worst case scenario, I need at least five more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's at all possible, hurry... and get\N some more for me, your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arf...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was scared and wanted nothing\N more to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need another, I can prepare\N you an even better familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never forget... that the person who's always\N truly on your side is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the ten days I spent with her went by so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lindy-san... I'm not sure whether to call what you're\N doing a wonderful cover-up or a complete lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I obviously can't tell them the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's so your family doesn't worry, so please\N call this my "consideration and concern."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nanoha-san is quite a good little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd almost like my son to learn from her example.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my... there you go, saying things like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Chrono just has no social skills whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sure that's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H333F94&\pos(320,425)}Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you came home today unexpectedly,\N you'll be able to stick around for a little, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.80,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alisa-chan and Suzuka-chan have also\N been really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten in touch with them yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I sent them both a message earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, send...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Alisa, did you receive a nice\N message or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. Just a normal text message.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samejima! Stop the car a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it was a big dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's injured... seriously injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samejima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, allow me to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're finally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? I've seen this girl somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a strong dog, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were hurt pretty badly, but you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until you're fully recovered, I'll take\N good care of you here at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can relax here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a friend of that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on. It's warm dog food... will you be able to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that hungry, I guess there's\N nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you finish eating, go to sleep so you\N can hurry up and get better, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha-chan! Thank goodness, you seem fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thanks, Suzuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to you too, Alisa-chan...\N making you worry about me while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess it's nice... to see that you're doing well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... so you'll have to leave again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be rough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but, everything will be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have time after school? Do you think\N we'll be able to play for a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... do you wanna come over to my house?\N I have a new video game...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that I think of it, I also\N found a hurt dog last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.02,0:14:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's really big, and its fur is kind of orange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a red jewel on its\N forehead shaped like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it really is you, Arf-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with those injuries?\N And also... where's Fate-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... it looks like she's lost her spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:15:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Are you feeling all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we just let her rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno! Hey now. That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Yuuno-kun will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nanoha, I'll hear the story from her myself,\N so you go with Alisa-chan and Suzuka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.68,0:15:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, do you wanna have some tea?\N I happened to have some really good tea inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.39,0:15:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what happened?\N What happened between you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you're here, then I guess the Administration\N Bureau is also watching, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chrono Hallaoun of the Time-Space\N Administration Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that your circumstances\N are quite complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you could explain them to me truthfully,\N I promise nothing bad will happen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen to either you\N or your master, Fate Testarossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll tell you... everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But promise me... promise me that you'll save Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That girl's done nothing wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise. Amy, start logging.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fate's mother... Precia Testarossa...\N is where everything begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use the item you just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one? Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nanoha... did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... I heard everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looking at your story, the current situation,\N and Arf's testimony and status...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...it would appear that her story\N was truthful and consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's gonna happen now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will arrest Precia Testarossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.30,0:16:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that she attacked the Asura\N is enough to warrant an arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:17:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now that we have an order from the captain,\N our mission will shift to focus on Precia's arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do now, Takamachi Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to save Fate-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.92,0:17:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of Arf-san's feelings...\N and also, because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever I see Fate with a sad look on her face,\N I somehow also become a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I want to save her...\N from all the sad things in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.30,0:17:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I told her I wanted to be friends...\N and I haven't heard her answer to that yet, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're also grateful that you're letting us\N continue to use your magical power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave everything regarding\N Fate Testarossa to you, Nanoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all right with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your name was... Nanoha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to be in your debt, but... but... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.37,0:17:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Save Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now... that girl really is all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah... it'll be fine. Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? We were waiting for you so\N we could enter this new dungeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It looks so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H333F94&\i1\pos(320,425)}As planned, you'll return to Asura tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it though?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use the time before then to\N do what you can about Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. I'm sure everything will turn out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H8D5E67&\pos(320,425)}He died...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... that really fired me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's so much more fun\N with you here, Nanoha-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.72,0:18:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I'll be done with things soon,\N so I'll be able to hang out all the time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you finally release that stress you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah? Umm... I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been worried about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the reason I was so angry at you wasn't because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were holding secrets, or because I couldn't\N understand what you were thinking, but rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you seemed so uneasy and lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got so bad that I thought you might not return to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll come right back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I'll be doing... is spending my time\N a little differently than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all so I can continue to be direct with\N myself about my feelings from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a small journey I must take\N so I don't regret anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You definitely look much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has your indecision finally faded away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew I was worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well of course I did. I'm your father, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to leave again early tomorrow morning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm sorry to make you worry again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know you're a strong girl,\N so I won't worry too much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, and stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please show yourself... Fate-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:55.55,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Scythe Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate... let's stop this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't listen to what that\N woman has to say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.21,0:22:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate... if you keep going like this,\N things will just get worse and worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... even so, I'm still her daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just throw away everything\N you've done so far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even consider running away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm pretty sure the Jewel Seeds are\N behind everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's bet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each of us will put our Jewel Seeds on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.22,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:53.72,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Put Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this... we can settle everything after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about us has yet to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... in order to truly start things between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.67,0:23:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...our true first and final match!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the silver wind came looking for\N two who were lacking something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:24:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the cellophane sea and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just crying in our city that's\N nothing more than a diorama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you held out to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ever-swaying years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt you looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I had finally, finally found the secret key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. Gather the lemon-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.22,0:24:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to gently light the path you're walking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.75,0:24:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.71,0:24:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then remember that because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:25:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.53,0:25:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I resolved to have a\N decisive battle with Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.48,0:25:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}And deep within it lies the\N connection between our pasts and presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.21,0:25:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}The Garden of Time which\N has been set in motion...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.75,0:25:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Just what is this Alhazred\N Precia wishes for?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.31,0:25:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time on\N Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.00,0:25:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Episode Eleven:\N Memories That Lie Beyond Time
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.14,0:25:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Lyrical Magical,\N full strength, going all out!
